response.original_title: The Marshall Tucker Band: Carolina Dreams Tour '77
response.overview: For some bands, the recording studio is everything and touring is an afterthought. This was definitely not the case for the Marshall Tucker band... Fortunately, the magical live chemistry of Marshall Tucker was captured on filme at a February 18, 1977 concert at Passaic, New Jersey's Capitol Theatre.
response.title: The Marshall Tucker Band: Carolina Dreams Tour '77
